title: Terence Blanchard
description:
A Conversation with Terence Blanchard, hosted by Rodney Whittenberg.
Recorded on Saturday, February 10, 2018 prior to Terence Blanchard's performance at Montgomery County Community College, Blue Bell, PA
tags: Terence Oliver Blanchard is an American jazz trumpeter
Blanchard started his career in 1980 as a member of the Lionel Hampton Orchestra
then Art Blakey and the Jazz Messengers
